---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Terms of Service — Lingo7"
  description="Lingo7 terms of service. Please read these terms carefully before using our application."
>
  <section class="legal-page">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="legal-content">
        <a href="/" class="back-link">&larr; Back to Home</a>

        <h1>Terms of Service</h1>
        <p class="last-updated">Last updated: December 22, 2026</p>

        <p>Welcome to Lingo7. By using our application, you agree to these Terms of Service. Please read them carefully.</p>

        <h2>1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
        <p>By downloading, installing, or using the Lingo7 application, you confirm that you have read, understood, and agree to comply with these Terms of Service.</p>

        <h2>2. Service Description</h2>
        <p>Lingo7 is a mobile application for learning foreign languages through parallel reading. We provide:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Texts in various languages with parallel translation</li>
          <li>Vocabulary memorization tools</li>
          <li>Learning progress tracking</li>
          <li>Personalized recommendations</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>3. Registration and Account</h2>
        <p>Some features of the application may require creating an account. You agree to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Provide accurate and up-to-date information</li>
          <li>Maintain the confidentiality of your account data</li>
          <li>Immediately notify us of any unauthorized access</li>
          <li>Be responsible for all activities under your account</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>4. Subscription and Payment</h2>
        <p>Some features of the application are available by subscription:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Subscriptions automatically renew unless cancelled at least 24 hours before the end of the current period</li>
          <li>Payment is charged through your App Store or Google Play account</li>
          <li>Subscription management is done through the app store settings</li>
          <li>Refunds are handled according to the respective store's policy</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>5. Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p>All content in the application, including texts, graphics, logos, icons, and software code, is protected by copyright and belongs to Lingo7 or our licensors. You may not:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Copy, modify, or distribute content without permission</li>
          <li>Use content for commercial purposes</li>
          <li>Decompile or reverse-engineer the application</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>6. Code of Conduct</h2>
        <p>When using the application, you may not:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Violate laws or the rights of third parties</li>
          <li>Transmit viruses or malicious code</li>
          <li>Attempt unauthorized access to the system</li>
          <li>Use the application for spam or fraud</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>7. Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
        <p>The application is provided "as is". We do not guarantee:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Uninterrupted operation of the application</li>
          <li>Absence of errors in the content</li>
          <li>Achievement of specific learning results</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>8. Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p>Lingo7 is not liable for indirect, incidental, or punitive damages arising from the use of the application, to the maximum extent permitted by law.</p>

        <h2>9. Changes to Terms</h2>
        <p>We reserve the right to modify these Terms. We will notify you of significant changes through the application. Continued use of the application after changes constitutes your acceptance of the new terms.</p>

        <h2>10. Termination</h2>
        <p>We may suspend or terminate your access to the application in case of violation of these Terms. You may stop using the application at any time by deleting it from your device.</p>

        <h2>11. Governing Law</h2>
        <p>These Terms are governed by applicable law. Disputes shall be resolved in the courts at the company's location.</p>

        <h2>12. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>For questions related to these Terms of Service, please contact us:</p>
        <p>Email: support@lingoseven.com</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .legal-page {
    padding: 120px 0 80px;
    min-height: 100vh;
  }
  .legal-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .legal-content h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    color: #ffffff;
  }
  .legal-content .last-updated {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }
  .legal-content h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 40px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    color: #ffffff;
  }
  .legal-content p,
  .legal-content li {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .legal-content ul {
    padding-left: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .legal-content li {
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .back-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    color: var(--primary);
    text-decoration: none;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    transition: opacity 0.3s;
  }
  .back-link:hover {
    opacity: 0.8;
  }
</style>
